<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.8.1">
<l>nallatōr tāmaraip poykai nāṇmalar mēlpaṉi cōra</l>
<l>alliyun tātumu tirntiṭ ṭaḻakaḻin tālot tatālō</l>
<l>illam veṟiyōṭiṟ ṟālō veṉmaka ḷaiyeṅkuṅ kāṇēṉ</l>
<l>mallarai yaṭṭavaṉ piṉpōy maturaip puṟampukkāḷ kolō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When dew drops on the day’s blossom in the lovely lotus pond,</l>
<l>[causing its] petals and pollen to fall away,</l>
<l rend="indent">is it not the case that [its] beauty is ruined?</l>
<l>[This] house has become mad, has it not?</l>
<l rend="indent">I don’t see my daughter anywhere!</l>
<l>Has she gone after the one who killed the wrestlers</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] entered the city of Mathurā?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
